from pygam import LinearGAM
# Extract gene expression and pseudotime
pseudotime = adata.obs["dpt_pseudotime"].values
expression_data = adata.X.toarray() if hasattr(adata.X, "toarray") else adata.X

# Store p-values and significance scores
p_values = []
gene_names = adata.var_names
spearman_rs = []
spearman_ps = []

# Fit GAM for each gene
for i, gene in enumerate(gene_names):
    gam = LinearGAM().fit(pseudotime, expression_data[:, i])
    p_val = gam.statistics_["p_values"][0]  # Get the p-value for the pseudotime coefficient
    p_values.append(p_val)
    spearman_r, spearman_p = scipy.stats.spearmanr(pseudotime, expression_data[:, i])
    spearman_rs.append(spearman_r)
    spearman_ps.append(spearman_p)
In [ ]:
import statsmodels
# Store results in a DataFrame
deg_results = pd.DataFrame({'gene': gene_names, 
                            'p_value': p_values,
                           'spearman_r': spearman_rs,
                           'spearman_p': spearman_ps})
deg_results['adjusted_p'] = statsmodels.stats.multitest.multipletests(deg_results['p_value'], alpha=0.05, method='fdr_bh', is_sorted=False, returnsorted=False)[1]# BH
deg_results['adjusted_spearman_p'] = statsmodels.stats.multitest.multipletests(deg_results['spearman_p'], alpha=0.05, method='fdr_bh', is_sorted=False, returnsorted=False)[1] # BH

# Filter significant DEGs (adjusted p-value < 0.05)
# deg_results = deg_results[deg_results['adjusted_p'] < 0.05].sort_values(by='adjusted_p')
# print(deg_results.head())

# Store significant DEGs in AnnData
adata.var["pseudotime_DEG"] = deg_results['gene'].isin(adata.var_names)

# top_degs = deg_results['gene'].values[:5]  # Change this number to see more genes
top_degs = ['Pcdhb11']
# Plot Expression Over Pseudotime
plt.figure(figsize=(8, 5))
for gene in top_degs:
    gene_idx = np.where(adata.var_names == gene)[0][0]
    smoothed_expr = LinearGAM().fit(pseudotime, expression_data[:, gene_idx]).predict(pseudotime)
    
    plt.plot(pseudotime, smoothed_expr, label=gene)
    plt.scatter(pseudotime, expression_data[:, gene_idx], label=gene)

plt.xlabel("Pseudotime")
plt.ylabel("Expression Level")
plt.title("Differentially Expressed Genes Over Pseudotime")
plt.legend()
plt.show()
